## Prerequisites  
Zenity must be installed:  
>> sudo apt install zenity  

## Build and Run  
>> make  
>> ./build/app  

## Configuration  
PLEASE CHANGE THE PATH GIVEN IN 'src/config/config.cpp' TO THE ACTUAL PATH TO THE PROJECT.  
Example:  
const std::string PATH_TO_PROJECT = "/path/to/your/project";  
Ensure this path reflects your project directory to avoid runtime issues.  
